<para xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="14" xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p1.s1">
For properties of zeros of <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p1.m1">\mathbf{H}_{\nu}\left(x\right)</Math> see Steinig (1970).
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="15" xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p2.s1">
For asymptotic expansions of zeros of <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C11.S4.SS7.p2.m1">\mathbf{H}_{0}\left(x\right)</Math> see MacLeod (2002a).
